from constituency\">{{cite news|title=All MLAs from constituency|publisher=elections.in|accessdate=November 2015|url=http://www.elections.in/uttar-pradesh/assembly-constituencies/sadabad.html}}</ref>\n\n==Early life and education==\nDevendra Agrawal was born in Hathras district. He attended the Gandhi Inter College, Mathura and is educated till [[tenth grade]].<ref name=\"Candidate affidavit\"/><ref name=\"Member  Profile\"/>\n\n==Political career==\nDevendra Agrawal has been a [[Member of the Legislative Assembly (India)|MLA]] for one term. He represented the [[Sadabad (Assembly constituency)|Sadabad]] constituency and is a member of the [[Samajwadi Party]] political party.<ref name=\"Member Profile\"/><ref name=\"Candidate affidavit\"/>\n\n==Posts held==\n{|  class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! # !! From !! To  !! Position !! Comments\n|-\n| 01 || 2012 ||  Incumbent || Member, [[16th Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh|16th Legislative Assembly]] ||\n|-\n|}\n\n==See also==\n* [[Sadabad (Assembly constituency)]]\n* [[Sixteenth Legislative Assembly of Uttar Pradesh]]\n* [[Uttar Pradesh Legislative Assembly]]\n\n{{Portal bar|India|Politics}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|colwidth=40em}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Agrawal, Devendra}}\n[[Category:Samajwadi Party politicians]]\n[[Category:Uttar Pradesh MLAs 2012\u20132017]]\n[[Category:People from Hathras district]]\n[[Category:1965 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2016}}\n{{Infobox officeholder\n | honorific-prefix        =\n | name                    =  Devendra Agrawal<br />\u0926\u0947\u0935\u0947\u0928\u094d\u0926\u094d\u0930 \u0905\u0917\u094d\u0930\u0935\u093e\u0932\n | honorific-suffix        =\n | image                   =\n | alt                     =\n | caption                 =\n | constituency            =   [[Sadabad (Assembly constituency)|Sadabad]]\n | office                  = [[Member of the Legislative Assembly (India)|MLA]], [[16th  Legislative Assembly of Ut